       pipeline {
       agent any
       stages {
       stage('Checkout Code') {
       steps {
       git branch:'main',url:'https://github.com/kavyathatavarthi/exp1-cli.git'
       }
       }
       stage('Print Message') {
       steps {
       echo 'Hello! Jenkins Pipeline executed successfully'
       }
       }
       }
      }
  iv)Write a Jenkins pipeline script to checkout code from a GitHub repository and create a new file using a batch command.
    ans::
     pipeline {
     agent any
     stages {
     stage('Checkout Code') {
     steps {
           git branch:'main',url:'https://github.com/kavyathatavarthi/exp1-cli.git'
     }
     }
     stage('Create File') {
     steps {
     bat 'echo This file is created by Jenkins > demo.txt'
     }
     }
     }
    }
